Members of Yin-Yang Karate and Self Defence Studio have not only participated and performed well during a recent all styles competition hosted in Louis Trichardt but they also graded to the next colour belt. During the competition the karatekas achieved six gold and 2 silver medals. In front are Alisha Patel, Musthapa Omar, Iqbal Patel and Jayden Heyns. In the middle are Thato Keipidile, Nusaybah Nagdi, Hamza Anver, Kwetsimane Mabunda and Manha Saleh with sensei Annatjie de Jager.
Photo: RC Myburgh